RelatedSentence: A man has been arrested on suspicion of murdering a woman who was found at a house in Barrow , Cumbria , on Sunday .

A spokeswoman for Cumbria Constabulary said : At 9.42 am today the North West Ambulance Service notified the police of a sudden death of a woman , in her 20 s , who had been found in a property on Napier Street , Barrow .
